Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.94,0:59:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Light\Nobserver, and then realize that observingness and witnessing it, and witnessingism, are
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.82,0:59:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,phenomena that are occurring of their own.\NNobody here decides whether they're going to be a witness or observer of the phenomena
