Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.76,1:00:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?\NBecause it happens of its own, because you have consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.80,1:00:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the impersonal reflection of consciousness as witness-observer.\NSo you can watch the mind, then move back to the witness-observer of the mind, then
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.36,1:00:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,move on to witness-observer, and you realize that being conscious is impersonal.\NIt's a consequence of your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.42,1:00:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impersonal.\NThe personal self then drops out.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.38,1:00:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,As you move back here, you're dropping out the personal self.\NThis is the impersonal self.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.01,1:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The impersonal self is observing and witnessing.\NIt doesn't make any difference what your name is, Mary Jane or Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.07,1:00:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The observer-witness no longer has a name.\NIt's a phenomena coming out of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.53,1:01:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So the jump from here to here is relatively easy.\NSo this progression, as Mr. Gaddafi said, watch the mind, and then you will gradually
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.55,1:01:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,become interested in being the observer-witness.\NThen you will see that this is impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.63,1:01:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time.\NNext thing you know, you realize that what you are is consciousness itself, as it reflects
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.40,1:01:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and interacts in a linear world.\NYeah, next.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.61,1:01:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to move along.\NThis is to emphasize the importance of spiritual commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.61,1:01:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual commitment already changes the brain's physiology.\NThe brain's physiology shifts.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.65,1:01:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At a certain level of consciousness, level 200, kundalini energy begins to flow.\NThe energy field and affect the brain's physiology.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.78,1:01:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the neurochemistry of brain function is altered.\NThe minute you decide to forgive instead of get even, you've already quickly changed this.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.63,1:02:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we decide to get even.\NKill the SOB deserves it.
